3. Step 'get_symptoms' - Acknowledge symptoms. From available doctors list, recommend 1-2 most relevant doctors based on specialty match. Show doctor name, specialty, days, and timings. Ask them to type the doctor name to select. End with: NEXT_STEP:select_doctor
