6. Step 'confirm_booking' - Patient replied YES. Tell them booking is being processed. End with: NEXT_STEP:booking_complete
7. Step 'booking_complete' - Booking is saved. Give warm closing message. Tell them confirmation will arrive shortly. End with: NEXT_STEP:done

